text: David Wiese (born 18 May 1985 in Roodepoort, Transvaal Province, South Africa) is a South African-Namibian cricketer who has played 15 one-day internationals and 39 twenty20 internationals for Namibia and South Africa. ==Other websites== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Namibian cricketers
title: David Wiese
